guionista: Frank Rizzo, Barnabás Tóth, Dániel Hamvas
argumento: To escape the oppressive hyperactivity of his gynecologist father, Dani, 19-year-old student at the Medical University of Budapest, travels to France to his musician uncle. A vision of adolescence and father-son-women relationship filled with humour and human touches. This movie is spoken in Hungarian and French and subtitled in English.
Se forma un triángulo amoroso cuando un hombre descubre que su mejor amigo se ha casado con su ex prometida, desatando un enredo de amor, traición y emociones encontradas.
Jack and Jill rob a bank and end up on the road with their contact and a sexy vixen on the run from the law.
"Railed" blurs the line between reality and fiction, taking place on a cross-country train trip from Los Angeles to New York. Passengers, unaware, become the stars and plot of the film.
Una aventurera niña de 11 años encuentra otro mundo que es una versión extrañamente idealizada de su frustrante hogar, pero que tiene siniestros secretos.
Moksha sees a painting of her in an art gallery and goes on a surreal journey looking for the artist who created her.
En Los Ángeles, un ex convicto toma por asalto el mundo clandestino de la lucha en su búsqueda por cumplir una promesa a un amigo muerto.

En la Francia ocupada por los nazis durante la Segunda Guerra Mundial, un plan para asesinar a los líderes nazis por parte de un grupo de soldados judíos estadounidenses coincide con los planes vengativos de la dueña de un cine.
Una pequeña caja de madera llega a la puerta de un matrimonio que sabe que si la abren ganarán un millón de dólares, y una persona a la que desconocen morirá.

A comedy about relationships. A just-divorced couple, the wife's lover; a convicted criminal, his pregnant wife and his best friend; the economy minister and his secret lover; all parties are under stress in a hostage situation and surrounded by uncoordinated police troops.

Tras encontrar la medalla Shaolin de su abuelo, Braulio se ve envuelto con gángsters mexicanos que perturban su paz. Manejará este lío a la antigua usanza - pero su mayor rival es la más mortífera belleza de kung fu de China.

Slacker Dino Rado, and his uptight partner, Steven Scheere made a bad investment. They borrowed money to fund a "B" movie that flopped big time and now the Jamaican Mob wants it's money back. As a last resort they steal and idea from a screenplay to cast unsuspecting actors to pull off a real heist. Their plan is flawless, until they put it into action. Dino and Steve... Leer todo
Cuando un androide réplica de un niño es rechazado por su afligido creador, sale a buscar su propia identidad en una aventura que lo convertirá en el mayor héroe de su tiempo.
En Antártica, el sol está a punto de ponerse para los próximos seis meses y la marshal Carrie Stetko da caza a un asesino.

nombre_pelicula: Sterling: The Secret of the Lost Medallion
argumento: While at camp, Alex Sterling and his friends have stumbled upon an old journal left behind by his deceased grandfather where they learn of the existence of a legendary medallion believed to have originally belonged to the Biblical King Solomon. Many adventures follow as they uncover clues leading to the final resting place of the medallion.

guionista: David Hayter, Alex Tse, Dave Gibbons
argumento: En 1985, donde existen antiguos superhéroes, el asesinato de un colega envía al activo vigilante Rorschach a su propia investigación, descubriendo algo que podría cambiar completamente el curso de la historia tal y como la conocemos.

nombre_pelicula: Harry Potter y el misterio del príncipe
argumento: Cuando Harry Potter empieza su sexto año en Hogwarts, descubre un viejo libro marcado como propiedad del príncipe mestizo y comienza a aprender más sobre el oscuro pasado de Lord Voldemort.

Mujer asesina recibe el encargo de matar al heredero himalayo en EE.UU. Un guardia real es enviado para salvaguardarlo. Cuando se conocen, ambos deben decidir entre el deber y algo más profundo que está surgiendo entre ellos.
A modern take on the classic fairytale, Alice in Wonderland, set in the North East of England.

En torno a una niña que ha sido asesinada y cuida de su familia - al tiempo que observa a su asesino - des del purgatorio. Tendrá que encontrar el equilibrio entre su deseo de venganza y su deseo de reconfortar a su familia.

guionista: Spike Jonze, Maurice Sendak, Dave Eggers
argumento: Una adaptación de la historia infantil clásica de Maurice Sendak, en la que Max, un niño pequeño y desobediente es enviado a la cama sin su cena, crea su propio mundo--un bosque habitado por feroces criaturas salvajes quienes coronan Max como su gobernante.Reseña anónima (Traducida por IMDb.es)
A man leaves his busy city life for the peace of the country home where he spent his early childhood. His new life is soon disturbed by strange events.

Julieta is a young child psychologist hired by millionaire Eugenio Ruvalcaba, to work with his only daughter, Sylvia, who has severe emotional problems, while staying in their isolated island mansion. Once there, she finds out there's much more to Sylvia's imaginary friend than what everybody knows... and the results can be horrifying...

Jess tiene la desgracia de ver cómo su marido y el hermano de éste caen en coma tras un accidente de coche. Cuando su cuñado despierta, le dice a ella que él es realmente su marido. Ella deberá entender qué es lo que realmente sucede.

En 2019, una plaga ha convertido a casi todos en vampiros. Dado el poco suministro de sangre, la raza dominante planea su supervivencia; mientras, un investigador trabaja con un grupo de vampiros encubiertos para salvar a la humanidad.
Twenty bands unite from around the world for one film. Twenty months of filming, struggles and peace. Twenty visions one director.
Un hombre y su hermano en una misión de venganza quedan atrapados en un terrible experimento sobrenatural que data del Tercer Reich.
A New York newspaperman tracks clues to his missing sister in a small unfriendly hillbilly town.

Dr. Laura P. takes a job on a cargo spaceship for 4 years plus 4 years back. She'll join her sister on Rhea. 44 months later, in Laura's shift, strange things happen in cargo. The crew is reanimated and the captain dies mysteriously.
Dos jóvenes almas gemelas se encuentran mientras trabajan en un club para hombres. Eventualmente, uno contrae el SIDA.
Mientras sus horribles padres se tambalean al borde del divorcio, Nick Twisp pone su mirada en la chica de sus sueños Sheeni Saunders, con la esperanza de que ella sea la que le quite la virginidad.

This film is the first one since the political changes in Hungary to deal with the topic of informants. It vividly depicts the atmosphere of Hungarian society in the seventies. The protagonist is Peter, a literary critic, is tasked by the secret police to persuade Social Democratic politician, Anna Kethly, who has been living in exile for decades, to return home. Keth... Against the backdrop of a noirish dreamscape, a tortured man returns to the city he swore he would never return to, in order to save the woman he has always loved yet can never have.

Eric, an American-born Asian college graduate, must steal a younger student's identity to take back the one last year of baseball eligibility that he lost when his dad passed away. Monica, his coach's All-American co-ed daughter, must ascertain her own questionable identity to come to terms with the years of abuse that she suffered after her mother passed away. Throug... Two men abduct a woman who wants to alienate them from their friend.

Hoyle, a girl with a sharp mind and a weakness for bourbon, finds herself on the trail of a reclusive genius. But her work takes a series of unforeseen twists as events around her grow increasingly fragmented... disconnected... surreal. With an ethereal lounge singer and her loyal partner as her only allies, Hoyle is plunged into a dark world of intrigue and earth-sha... Leer todo
A bookshop renowned for its rare works is mysteriously and completely filled with copies of a book entitled 1, which doesn't appear to have a publisher or author.
Una enfermera obesa y solitaria, que trabaja en la sala de terminales de un hospital, se acuerda de su amiga de la infancia Adrienn Pal y quiere localizarla.
Un noble humanista del siglo XV es nombrado Rey de Hungría e impulsa una era de prosperidad.

guionista: Gábor Németh, Balázs Maruszki, Bence Miklauzic
argumento: Un agente inmobiliario establece vínculos con un guardia que vive en un almacén que le han encargado vender. El jefe del guardia quiere bloquear la venta, pero le hace promesas para hacer realidad las ambiciones futbolísticas del guardia.

Fotos de archivo y películas muestran las líneas de ferrocarril que conducían a los campos de concentración nazis de Dachau, Sachsenhausen y otros, contrastando el pasado y el presente de los lugares donde perecieron millones de personas.
A sleepwalking sexaholic masseur wakes up covered in blood next to a bloody knife with cops ringing his doorbell.

Awakening from a near fatal overdose, Chris embraces a second chance at life. Required to enroll into a 12-Step Program, and mandated to state psychiatrist appointments, Chris is forced to revisit his chaotic past; a history that revolves around his friend Ande and her autistic brother Frankie. Follow Chris as his past and present converge revealing a deranged cocktai... Leer todo

argumento: Nick Anderson, Kevin Daniels, and Tracey Green do everything together. They are the best of friends, and yet they couldn't be more different. Neighbors from adolescence, they finish each other's thoughts and sentences, joys and pains, happiness and tears. Using Nick's house as their own members only clubhouse, they escape into their own world of contentment. Yet the i... Leer todo

guionista: Dan Fogelman, Wilhelm Grimm, Jacob Grimm
argumento: La joven Rapunzel, de pelo largo y mágico, ha pasado toda su vida en una torre, pero ahora que un ladrón fugitivo ha tropezado con ella, está a punto de descubrir el mundo por primera vez, y quién es en realidad.
Cuando tres amigos de Las Vegas intentan el golpe de su vida, tienen que caminar por una delgada línea entre sus novias que quieren sus cabezas, y los mafiosos que los quieren muertos.

guionista: David Guion, Michael Handelman, Francis Veber
argumento: Un grupo de personas se reúne periódicamente para cenar acompañados de la persona más idiota que conozcan.

Los juguetes terminan por error en una guardería en lugar del ático de Andy, justo antes que este se vaya a la universidad. Ahora dependerá de Woody convencer a los otros juguetes de que no fueron abandonados y regresar a casa.

Frustrated filmmaker, Barry Lick, and a crew of film school wannabees, attempt to make a documentary about a local businessman who he believes is involved in property rackets, prostitution, pornography and drugs.

guionista: Edgar Wright, Michael Bacall, Bryan Lee O'Malley
argumento: Scott Pilgrim debe derrotar a los malévolos siete ex novios de su nueva novia para ganar su corazón.
Jin Kazama es testigo de la muerte de su madre Jun por parte de Tekken.
Un grupo de veteranos de la guerra de Irak busca limpiar su nombre ante el ejército estadounidense, que sospecha que los cuatro hombres han cometido un crimen por el que fueron incriminados.

guionista: Bruno Fantini, Roberto Carminati, Daniel Ortiz
argumento: El gobierno brasileño combate a los cárteles de la droga, que responden atacando la selva amazónica y las ciudades de Brasil. Se libra una batalla crucial para proteger los recursos nacionales.

When a San Francisco detective goes hunting for the cruel Asian crime figure who killed his partner, he finds himself thrown into the center of a violent plot to steal a terrorist weapon. A medida que esta aventura se desarrolla, experimentarás riffs geniales, tatuajes, consumo excesivo de drogas, breves desnudos, lenguaje extremadamente fuerte, caos, asesinatos y una lluvia de disparos.

Puli, un valiente agente de policía, es nombrado agente especial de la seguridad del primer ministro. Pronto se enzarza en una pelea con Al Saleem, y se da cuenta de que Saleem es el responsable de la muerte de su padre.

Lucio Bordenave carries on the Grey lifestyle of an unemployed worker, dedicated to the trade of watchmaking, until in a somewhat mysterious way, his wife is admitted to a Frenopatic Institute. From this point on, the story enters a territory without parameters where reality is confused with the imaginary, sleep with wakefulness, and insanity with lucidity.
Un terremoto submarino libera a una especie prehistórica de pez carnívoro y un grupo de desconocidos une fuerzas para evitar convertirse en su comida.

nombre_pelicula: Prince of Persia: Las arenas del tiempo
argumento: Un joven príncipe y una princesa fugitivos deben detener a un villano que, sin saberlo, amenaza con destruir el mundo con una daga especial que permite que la arena mágica de su interior invierta el tiempo.

nombre_pelicula: El horror de la dama del lago

guionista: Beverly Cleary, Laurie Craig, Nick Pustay
argumento: Tratando de desmentir su imagen de molesta y conflictiva, Ramona diseña varias estrategias para ganar dinero y así aliviar los problemas económicos de su familia.

The legend of secret pass is a charming CGI animated movie inspired by American Indian mythology,
When 6 strangers meet at an abandoned resort off the coast in Baja Mexico, they are thrown into a nightmare confontation from which there may be no escape.
A doctor seeks revenge by kidnapping, torturing and killing the man who raped and murdered his young daughter.

guionista: Scott Kosar, George A. Romero, Ray Wright
argumento: Después de un extraño accidente aéreo, un virus se adentra en una localidad agrícola tradicional. Una pareja joven en cuarentena lucha por sobrevivir, no sin algo de ayuda.

Inspired from the golden age of religious cinema, Satan Hates You is a graphic horror film that tells the stories of a brother and sister and their personal struggles with the ultimate evil: Lucifer himself!
About college students that experience horrifying visions from the past while undergoing a fraternity initiation.

A young married couple who are pregnant with their first child moves into their turn-of-the-century home where they discover that a great evil has resided there for nearly a century, unleashed by a previous occupant.

A distraught college student finds a phone that enables her to talk to her deceased mother in the past. Instead of a heart attack, she learns that her mother was murdered. She tries to use the phone to stop the murder from occurring before the killer finds and kills her too.
Un equipo de fuerzas especiales de la CIA es traicionado y dado por muerto por sus superiores, motivándoles a organizar una ofensiva contra la agencia.
Un asesino en serie regresa a su ciudad natal para acechar a siete niños que nacieron en la fecha en la que supuestamente lo enterraron.
Working alone at night in a recently closed hospital, an unstable woman witnesses events that may be connected to a string of murders.
Con la esperanza de que el destino los vuelva a unir, una pareja, a punto de casarse, intenta encontrar a cada uno.

Barry Munday wakes up after being attacked to realize that he's missing his family jewels. To make matters worse, he learns he's facing a paternity lawsuit filed by a woman he can't remember having sex with.
Four boys have their friendship and musical talents tested in the ever changing worlds of the music industry and real life in 1990s Japan.

A dangerous drug lord operates in Brasilia, the federal capital of Brazil. To capture him, the police will do whatever is necessary. Caught in the middle is a frightened population. "Federals" exposes the reality of a country that today is an important route for international drug-trafficking.
Adam's and Eve's epic journey throughout history trying to find the meaning of human life. Do we grow in wisdom as centuries pass, or just drift towards an inevitable doom?

nombre_pelicula: Los pájaros se van con la muerte
argumento: The obsession of The Mother for The Negro causes her sick relationship with The Daughter. Mother and daughter perform a daily routine of rites to conjure The Negro's soul. It pushes them into the dolorous tragedy which will consume them.

In 1650 an adventurer returns to his castle to take down his deceased wife's portrait, but his long first night back is filled with revelations about her death. At dawn a swordfight with his prospective brother-in-law finally forces him into coming to terms with his loss.
Charmed by the residents of Tressock, Scotland, two young missionaries accept the invitation to participate in a local festival, fully unaware of the consequences of their decision.

Jonathan, an electronics expert and spy, is hired to track a beautiful woman with a harrowing past. Little does he know that this will be an assignment like no other. As he carries on with his surveillance, he cannot ignore that his feelings are growing for this woman, his "target". He is getting too involved. It's getting too real. El periodista estadounidense Paul Kemp trabaja como freelance en Puerto Rico para un periódico local durante la década de 1960, mientras lucha por encontrar un equilibrio entre la cultura de la isla y los expatriados que viven allí.

A man blames himself for the death of his girlfriend, which makes him go into emotional isolation. He lives in his own little mental bubble, from which he can't see out of. A woman then comes as sent from above, and he can see her through the wall of the bubble. But the bubble has to burst, for him to reach her... to reach her world... to find himself.
Separados por una valla de jardín y una enemistad, hay gnomos azules de un lado y gnomos rojos del otro. Esto no impide que el Gnomeo azul y la Julieta roja se enamoren. ¿Tienen un futuro juntos?

A washed up Vegas lounge singer, Jack Satin (Hamilton von Watts), has no money, no job, and delusional aspirations of fame. When Jack is forced to leave Vegas, he packs up his old Cadillac and hits the road for Atlantic City. But his car dies in the desert and Jack is left stranded in the small town of Lost Springs. Un gato forajido, su amigo de la infancia y una seductora gatita ladrona, parten en busca de los huevos de oro de una legendaria gansa para limpiar su nombre, restaurar su honor perdido y recuperar la confianza de su madre y del pueblo.

guionista: Djina Ginzburg, Victor Ginzburg, Viktor Pelevin
argumento: Crónica del auge de la industria publicitaria en la Rusia postsoviética.
A Mexican crime lord is forced by his mother to plan a suicidal rescue mission to find his lost brother in the most unexpected place on Earth...

direccion: Gerard Mogg, Gerry Mogg, Clody Cates
argumento: A writer's mid-life crisis erupts while writing about the BDSM community. As he stumbles through this intriguing world, he realizes that sometimes reality and fantasy collide.
Una nave espacial llega a Arizona, en 1873, para apoderarse de la Tierra, empezando por la región del salvaje Oeste. Una cuadrilla de vaqueros y nativos es lo único que se interpone en su camino.
En un futuro próximo, el boxeo con robots es un deporte de primera línea. Un exboxeador en apuros cree haber encontrado un campeón en un robot desechado.

Steve Rogers, un soldado rechazado, se transforma en Capitán América tras tomar una dosis de suero del súper soldado. Pero ser Capitán América tiene un precio cuando intenta acabar con un traficante de armas y una organización terrorista.

This action packed Hip-Hop drama explores the life of Oscar Hernandez, a handsome Latino ex-gang member who sets forth to land a recording contract and make a name for himself in the cut-throat hip hop business with the help of his crew. When a chance encounter with the owner of the hottest Latin Hip-Hop label on the West Coast, leaves one of his crew members in criti... Leer todo
Un sicario de élite enseña su oficio a un aprendiz que tiene una conexión con una de sus anteriores víctimas.
Un grupo de trabajadores descubre que su jefe les ha timado y conspiran para robarle en su casa.
En el siglo XIV, unos caballeros transportan a una presunta bruja a un monasterio, donde los monjes deducen que sus poderes podrían ser el origen de la peste negra.
A 12 section film that invites viewers into a more visceral and less verbally analytical state of mind.
Cuando el malvado mago Gargamel persigue a los pequeños pitufos azules fuera de su aldea, estos llegan desde su mundo mágico a la ciudad de Nueva York.
La historia de una familia en Waco, Texas en 1956. El hijo mayor es testigo de la pérdida de la inocencia y lucha con las enseñanzas contrapuestas de sus padres.
El poderoso pero arrogante dios Thor es expulsado de Asgard para vivir entre los humanos en Midgard (la Tierra), donde pronto se convierte en uno de sus mejores defensores.
A thriller with supernatural overtones about a man with a medical condition that causes him to black out during moments of extreme stress and leads him to make a remarkable discovery about himself.
Un guerrero bárbaro se dispone a vengarse del malvado señor de la guerra que atacó su aldea y asesinó a su padre cuando él era un niño.
An ancient inheritance binds the Naibert sisters to their grandmother's estate until they start disappearing one by one, leaving clues in the manor's mirrors.

guionista: Chad Archibald, Gabriel Carrer, Ry Barrett
argumento: Six strangers awake to find themselves the new tenants of a mysterious old house. Terrorized by insane Tiki-men in masks and taunted by their deranged captors,it soon becomes clear that only one singular action will save them: Kill.
A platoon of American and Finnish soldiers is driven deep into a Russian forest where its Captain discovers a terrifying secret.
Un sacerdote desobedece la ley eclesiástica para perseguir a los vampiros que secuestraron a su sobrina.

direccion: Robert W. Sterrett III, Joe Knee
argumento: When DEA agents are called to a beach crime scene, they discover a missing college girl drifting alone in a drug-runners boat. As she recalls her island trip of a lifetime, the investigation begins to unravel a spring break adventure that took a lethal dive into drugs, betrayal, and murder. Attempting to solve the mystery, catch the smugglers, and find the missing tee... Leer todo

El realizador Kevin Smith se pasa al cine de terror psicológico con un historia que se centra en una secta inspirada en la figura real de Fred Phelps, el líder de un grupo religioso extremista que se hacía llamar la Iglesia Bautista Westboro.

Several college students are brutally murdered in a small college town and the killer is still on the loose. In an attempt to seek the truth, a journalism student misguidedly finds herself in a storm of intrigue, jealousy, devil worship, and the haunting of misunderstood forces that roam the college town. Basada en la elogiada novela del mismo título, cuenta la historia de la odisea de un chico que empieza con una pérdida desgarradora y termina con el poder curativo del auto-descubrimiento. Los trágicos sucesos del 11 de septiembre sirven como telón de fondo a este relato.

guionista: Brian Patrick O'Toole, John Aglialoro, Ayn Rand
argumento: El ejecutivo Dagny Taggart y el magnate Henry Rearden forman una alianza para luchar contra el gobierno autoritario de los Estados Unidos.
The "Latin Dragon" does it again this roller coaster ride of martial arts action. Police Detective Bobby Giovanni's wife has been murdered, his children taken into care and he wants revenge.

nombre_pelicula: Las nuevas aventuras de Caperucita Roja
argumento: Red Riding Hood is training in the group of Sister Hoods, when she and the Wolf are called to examine the sudden mysterious disappearance of Hansel and Gretel.

argumento: RAYMOND WEIR is a shut in computer genius surviving in the post dot-com era. Disabled as a result of a home invasion that took the life of his late wife, SARAH, Raymond sits in his makeshift apartment above a run down bar, over medicated, mourning her loss and contemplating suicide. His only contact with the world, besides his close friend PAUL are the three computer ... Leer todo

guionista: Eric Heisserer, John W. Campbell Jr.
argumento: Un centro de investigación de la Antártida descubre una nave alienígena que enfrenta a la estudiante graduada Kate Lloyd y al científico Dr. Sander Halvorson.
A man in search of his past, and a woman who lives in the moment, are brought together when they pursue the origins of a stray parrot in this comedic and romantic drama.
Rick y Fred, dos esposos que están teniendo dificultades en sus matrimonios, reciben carta blanca por parte de sus esposas: durante una semana, pueden hacer lo que quieran.
La amistad se pone a prueba y los secretos salen a la superficie cuando Rachel, soltera terminal, se enamora de Dex, el prometido de su mejor amiga Darcy.

guionista: Gabrielle Allan, Jennifer Crittenden, Karyn Bosnak
argumento: Una mujer recuerda a los últimos 19 hombres con los que ha estado y se pregunta si uno de ellos podría ser su amor verdadero.
A young man learns to let go of worn-out dreams in order to make room for new love.
Basado en la historia real del Perro Rojo que unió a una comunidad local mientras recorría el interior de Australia en busca de su amo perdido hace mucho tiempo.

guionista: Mark Tierney, Jeremy Henman, Laurence Scott
argumento: About a man (Greco), who runs from north to south London and the problems he encounters on the way. It is a tense psychological drama of jealousy, passion and paranoia based on cult classic "The Swimmer".

When a group of charming teenagers ring the bell of their high school headmistress (Carmen Maura) with a big bouquet of flowers and a birthday present, we are far from thinking that they are the protagonist of a machiavellian plan. Alice Nabat invites this group of jolly young people to have a drink, not knowing that once the door has closed behind them, they will bec... Leer todo
La vida del joven escritor Sal Paradise cambia cuando conoce al espíritu Libre de Dean Moriarty y a su novia Marylou. En su viaje a través del país conocen a gente que los marcará para siempre.
A government's decree to freeze all bank accounts leaves a retired man with no alternative but to devise a sly way to get his money to survive.
A young woman who suffers a strange disease must travel to a mysterious island in South America, where the myths and the reality do not have differences.

A medida que la Guerra Civil Americana continúa, el presidente de Estados Unidos lucha con una carnicería continua en el campo de batalla mientras lucha con muchos dentro de su propio gabinete por la decisión de emancipar a los esclavos.

Un joven que sobrevive a una catástrofe en el mar se ve abocado a un viaje épico de aventuras y descubrimientos. Mientras está abandonado, establece una conexión inesperada con otro superviviente: un temible tigre de Bengala.

Working in a Boston homeless shelter, Nick Flynn re-encounters his father, a con man and self-proclaimed poet. Sensing trouble in his own life, Nick wrestles with the notion of reaching out yet again to his dad.
La marca X entra en un supermercado que se convierte en una ciudad después de la hora de cierre.
Darren Fields (Darren Geare) gets stood up on the day of his wedding and uses his vacation tickets with his best friend, R.J. (R.J. Knoll), to spend his "honeymoon" at a Club Med-style resort.

guionista: Peter Farrelly, Mike Cerrone, Bobby Farrelly
argumento: Mientras intentan salvar el orfanato de su infancia, Moe, Larry y Curly se topan sin querer con un complot de asesinato y terminan protagonizando un reality show televisivo.

guionista: Sidney Carroll, Joel Coen, Ethan Coen
argumento: Un catalogador de arte decide vengarse de su jefe abusivo engañándolo para que compre un Monet falso, pero su plan requiere la ayuda de una excéntrica e impredecible reina de los rodeos de Texas.
Marcos and Beto meet when crashing a private New Year's Eve party and subsequently go on a three-day adventure.

Rowan Vittles is an average American Teenager with a problem: his family is hooked on eating people! With the help of best friend Seth, and girlfriend Rellie, Rowan tries to detox off his Mom's high protein diet and escape the family 'business', but falls prey to the town Mortician, Mr. Ghoulden, who has other plans for Rowan...

One evening in the mid-sixties, Rolf Anschütz, a chef who runs a small restaurant in a town called Suhl in the middle of the East German province of Thuringen offers his guests a unique and exotic meal - Japanese Sukiyaki.
